Breakfree Audio TuneBlade v1.3.5 [deepstatus]

TuneBlade is a simple tray utility that lets you stream system-wide
audio to AirPort Express, Apple TV, AirPlay enabled speakers and HiFi
receivers, and to AirPlay audio receiving applications such as
ShairPort, XBMC/Kodi and TuneAero



[INSTALLATION]


- Unrar with you favorite archiver, such as WinRar

- Install Setup.exe

- Use included keygen to make valid unlock code(s).

- Ok, It's Activated!
